Not only does he operate Earth's most sophisticated battlesuit as Iron Man, but in the wake of the Civil War he's also the new director of S.H.I.E.L.D.--all at the cost of his personal life and relationships. A book filled with hi-tech action, political intrigue and emotional resonance, Iron Man delivers the goods!
